Media query:
apply the style only if the width of the screen is over 500px
1. HTML: <link rel="stylesheet" media = "screen and {min-width: 500px)" href="yes.css">
2. CSS: @media screen and (min-width: 500px) {
	body {background-color:green};
	}
3. do not use "min-device-width" "max-device-width" for media query